    "translatedContent": "| `tailscale_hostname` | Nom d’hôte à enregistrer auprès de Tailscale.                                                  | **Oui**     | N/A         |"
  },
  {
    "row": 97,
    "rowsha": "KI3MoAQDN4VViwXqtVLVbu0QAl2AzXlo5z2XaTM1t8Y=",
    "originContent": "| `tailscale_tags`     | Tags to advertise to Tailscale (e.g. `tag:nix-ci-builder`).                                     | **Yes**  | N/A         |",
    "translatedContent": "| `tailscale_tags`     | Tags à annoncer à Tailscale (ex. `tag:nix-ci-builder`).                                        | **Oui**     | N/A         |"
  },
  {
    "row": 98,
    "rowsha": "knWQDP6lPESY+QzlzHAQEUw79+oxJhZi9Xl6Vq5/zxk=",
