    "originContent": "| `builders`           | Space separated list of full builder hostnames to wait for. (_Required if role is coordinator_) | No       | `\"\"`        |",
    "translatedContent": "| `builders`           | Liste d’hôtes complets des builders à attendre, séparés par des espaces. (_Requis si rôle coordinator_) | Non         | `\"\"`        |"
